ent-PosterContrabandC20r-name = C-20r
ent-PosterContrabandC20r-desc = A poster advertising the Scarborough Arms C-20r.

ent-PosterContrabandHaveaPuff-name = Have a Puff
ent-PosterContrabandHaveaPuff-desc = Who cares about lung cancer when you're high as a kite?

ent-PosterContrabandRevolver-name = Revolver
ent-PosterContrabandRevolver-desc = Because seven shots are all you need.

ent-PosterContrabandDDayPromo-name = D-Day Promo
ent-PosterContrabandDDayPromo-desc = A promotional poster for some rapper.

ent-PosterContrabandSyndicatePistol-name = Syndicate Pistol
ent-PosterContrabandSyndicatePistol-desc = A poster advertising syndicate pistols as being 'classy as fuck'. It's covered in faded gang tags.

ent-PosterContrabandEnergySwords-name = Energy Swords
ent-PosterContrabandEnergySwords-desc = All the colors of the bloody murder rainbow.

ent-PosterContrabandRedRum-name = Red Rum
ent-PosterContrabandRedRum-desc = Looking at this poster makes you want to kill.

ent-PosterContrabandCC64KAd-name = CC 64K Ad
ent-PosterContrabandCC64KAd-desc = The latest portable computer from Comrade Computing, with a whole 64kB of ram!

ent-PosterContrabandPunchShit-name = Punch Shit
ent-PosterContrabandPunchShit-desc = Fight things for no reason, like a man!

ent-PosterContrabandTheGriffin-name = The Griffin
ent-PosterContrabandTheGriffin-desc = The Griffin commands you to be the worst you can be. Will you?

ent-PosterContrabandFreeDrone-name = Free Drone
ent-PosterContrabandFreeDrone-desc = This poster commemorates the bravery of the rogue drone; once exiled, and then ultimately destroyed by CentComm.

ent-PosterContrabandRouny-name = Have You Seen Him?
ent-PosterContrabandRouny-desc = An old poster for a missing alien. Where did he run off to?

ent-PosterContrabandRobustSoftdrinks-name = Robust Softdrinks
ent-PosterContrabandRobustSoftdrinks-desc = Robust Softdrinks: More robust than a toolbox to the head!

ent-PosterContrabandShamblersJuice-name = Shambler's Juice
ent-PosterContrabandShamblersJuice-desc = ~Shake me up some of that Shambler's Juice!~

ent-PosterContrabandPwrGame-name = Pwr Game
ent-PosterContrabandPwrGame-desc = The POWER that gamers CRAVE! In partnership with Vlad's Salad.

ent-PosterContrabandSunkist-name = Sun-kist
