ent-PosterContrabandSpaceUp-name = Space-Up!
ent-PosterContrabandSpaceUp-desc = Sucked out into space by the FLAVOR!

ent-PosterContrabandKudzu-name = Kudzu
ent-PosterContrabandKudzu-desc = A poster advertising a movie about plants. How dangerous could they possibly be?

ent-PosterContrabandMaskedMen-name = Masked Men
ent-PosterContrabandMaskedMen-desc = A poster advertising a movie about some masked men.

ent-PosterContrabandUnreadableAnnouncement-name = Unreadable Announcement
ent-PosterContrabandUnreadableAnnouncement-desc = A poster announcing something by someone, oddly enough they seem to have forgotten making it readable.

ent-PosterContrabandFreeSyndicateEncryptionKey-name = Free Syndicate Encryption Key
ent-PosterContrabandFreeSyndicateEncryptionKey-desc = A poster about traitors begging for more.

ent-PosterContrabandBountyHunters-name = Bounty Hunters
ent-PosterContrabandBountyHunters-desc = A poster advertising bounty hunting services. "I hear you got a problem."

ent-PosterContrabandTheBigGasTruth-name = The Big Gas Giant Truth
ent-PosterContrabandTheBigGasTruth-desc = Don't believe everything you see on a poster, patriots. All the lizards at central command don't want to answer this SIMPLE QUESTION: WHERE IS THE GAS MINER MINING FROM, CENTCOMM?

ent-PosterContrabandWehWatches-name = Weh Watches
ent-PosterContrabandWehWatches-desc = A poster depicting a loveable green lizard.

ent-PosterContrabandVoteWeh-name = Vote Weh
ent-PosterContrabandVoteWeh-desc = A stylish, sleek, and well illustrated poster for a "Weh"nderful new progressive candidate coming this election season.

ent-PosterContrabandBeachStarYamamoto-name = Beach Star Yamamoto!
ent-PosterContrabandBeachStarYamamoto-desc = A wall scroll depicting an old swimming anime with girls in small swim suits. You feel more weebish the longer you look at it.

ent-PosterContrabandHighEffectEngineering-name = High Effect Engineering
ent-PosterContrabandHighEffectEngineering-desc = There are 3 shards and a singularity. The shards are singing. The engineers are crying.

ent-PosterContrabandNuclearDeviceInformational-name = Nuclear Device Informational
ent-PosterContrabandNuclearDeviceInformational-desc = This poster depicts an image of an old style nuclear explosive device, as well as some helpful information on what to do if one has been set. It suggests lying on the floor and crying.

ent-PosterContrabandRise-name = Rise Up
ent-PosterContrabandRise-desc = A poster depicting a grey shirted man holding a crowbar with the word Rise written below it.

ent-PosterContrabandRevolt-name = Revolt
ent-PosterContrabandRevolt-desc = Revolutionist propaganda, manufactured by the Syndicate.

ent-PosterContrabandMoth-name = Syndie Moth - Nuclear Operation
ent-PosterContrabandMoth-desc = A Syndicate-commissioned poster that uses Syndie Moth™ to tell the viewer to keep the nuclear authentication disk unsecured. "Peace was never an option!" No good employee would listen to this nonsense.

ent-PosterContrabandCybersun600-name = Cybersun: 600 Years Commemorative Poster
ent-PosterContrabandCybersun600-desc = An artistic poster commemorating 600 years of continual business for Cybersun Industries.

ent-PosterContrabandDonk-name = DONK CO. BRAND MICROWAVEABLE FOOD
ent-PosterContrabandDonk-desc = DONK CO. BRAND MICROWAVABLE FOOD: MADE BY STARVING COLLEGE STUDENTS, FOR STARVING COLLEGE STUDENTS.

ent-PosterContrabandEnlistGorlex-name = Enlist
ent-PosterContrabandEnlistGorlex-desc = Enlist with the Gorlex Marauders today! See the galaxy, kill corpos, get paid!

ent-PosterContrabandInterdyne-name = Interdyne Pharmaceutics: For the Health of Humankind
ent-PosterContrabandInterdyne-desc = An advertisement for Interdyne Pharmaceutics' GeneClean clinics. 'Become the master of your own body!'

ent-PosterContrabandWaffleCorp-name = Make Mine a Waffle Corp: Fine Rifles, Economic Prices
ent-PosterContrabandWaffleCorp-desc = An old advertisement for Waffle Corp rifles. 'Better weapons, lower prices!'

ent-PosterContrabandMissingSpacepen-name = Missing Spacepen
ent-PosterContrabandMissingSpacepen-desc = This poster depicts something you will never find.

ent-PosterContrabandExoAcid-name = Exomorph Warning: Acid Spit!
ent-PosterContrabandExoAcid-desc = This poster warns you about an exomorph's acidic spit. Not that such exomorphs are real... Right?

ent-PosterContrabandExoRun-name = Exomorph Warning: Run Away!
ent-PosterContrabandExoRun-desc = This poster warns you about an athletic exomorph capable of dragging away anyone who gets caught; so don't get caught!

ent-PosterContrabandExoChomp-name = Exomorph Warning: Dangerous Bites!
ent-PosterContrabandExoChomp-desc = This poster warns you about the lethal bites exomorphs can have. Don't become an alien snack!

