ent-PosterLegitWalk-name = Walk
ent-PosterLegitWalk-desc = A poster instructing the viewer to walk instead of running.

ent-PosterLegitStateLaws-name = State Laws
ent-PosterLegitStateLaws-desc = A poster instructing cyborgs to state their laws.

ent-PosterLegitLoveIan-name = Love Ian
ent-PosterLegitLoveIan-desc = Ian is love, Ian is life.

