ent-PosterLegitDoNotQuestion-name = Do Not Question
ent-PosterLegitDoNotQuestion-desc = A poster instructing the viewer not to ask about things they aren't meant to know.

ent-PosterLegitWorkForAFuture-name = Work For A Future
ent-PosterLegitWorkForAFuture-desc = A poster encouraging you to work for your future.

ent-PosterLegitSoftCapPopArt-name = Soft Cap Pop Art
ent-PosterLegitSoftCapPopArt-desc = A poster reprint of some cheap pop art.

ent-PosterLegitSafetyInternals-name = Safety: Internals
ent-PosterLegitSafetyInternals-desc = A poster instructing the viewer to wear internals in the rare environments where there is no oxygen or the air has been rendered toxic.

ent-PosterLegitSafetyEyeProtection-name = Safety: Eye Protection
ent-PosterLegitSafetyEyeProtection-desc = A poster instructing the viewer to wear eye protection when dealing with chemicals, smoke, or bright lights.

ent-PosterLegitSafetyReport-name = Safety: Report
ent-PosterLegitSafetyReport-desc = A poster instructing the viewer to report suspicious activity to the security force.

ent-PosterLegitReportCrimes-name = Report Crimes
