ent-PosterLegitCohibaRobustoAd-name = Cohiba Robusto Ad
ent-PosterLegitCohibaRobustoAd-desc = Cohiba Robusto, the classy cigar.

ent-PosterLegit50thAnniversaryVintageReprint-name = 50th Anniversary Vintage Reprint
ent-PosterLegit50thAnniversaryVintageReprint-desc = A reprint of a poster from 2505, commemorating the 50th Anniversary of Nanoposters Manufacturing, a subsidiary of Nanotrasen.

ent-PosterLegitFruitBowl-name = Fruit Bowl
ent-PosterLegitFruitBowl-desc = Simple, yet awe-inspiring.

ent-PosterLegitPDAAd-name = PDA Ad
ent-PosterLegitPDAAd-desc = A poster advertising the latest PDA from Nanotrasen suppliers.

ent-PosterLegitEnlist-name = Enlist
ent-PosterLegitEnlist-desc = Enlist in the Nanotrasen Deathsquadron reserves today!

ent-PosterLegitNanomichiAd-name = Nanomichi Ad
ent-PosterLegitNanomichiAd-desc = A poster advertising Nanomichi brand audio cassettes.

ent-PosterLegit12Gauge-name = 12 gauge
ent-PosterLegit12Gauge-desc = A poster boasting about the superiority of 12 gauge shotgun shells.

ent-PosterLegitHighClassMartini-name = High-Class Martini
ent-PosterLegitHighClassMartini-desc = I told you to shake it, no stirring.

ent-PosterLegitTheOwl-name = The Owl
ent-PosterLegitTheOwl-desc = The Owl would do his best to protect the station. Will you?

ent-PosterLegitNoERP-name = No ERP
ent-PosterLegitNoERP-desc = This poster reminds the crew that Eroticism and Pornography are banned on Nanotrasen stations.

